<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Fabrication_joint_mim.connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint">
<p>

A <b>connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="Fabrication_joint:mim:Fabrication_joint_mim.fabrication_joint"/> that includes the
identification of the connection zones that are to be mated in addition to the specific
features that are to be mated.  A <b>connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint</b> implements the ARM
concept of <express_ref linkend="Fabrication_joint:arm:Fabrication_joint_arm.Connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint"/>.

</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Fabrication_joint_mim.connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint.wr:WR1">
The <b>connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint</b> shall be related to exactly one  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> as 'zone 1' by
a  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/>.<express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.related_shape_aspect"/>. 
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Fabrication_joint_mim.connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint.wr:WR2">
The <b>connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint</b> shall be related to exactly one  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> as 'zone 2' by
a  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/>.<express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/>.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint.WR3
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Fabrication_joint_mim.connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint.wr:WR3">
The <b>connection_zone_based_fabrication_joint</b> shall be related to only <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect">shape_aspects</express_ref> with a description of 'connection zone'. 
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Entity: fabrication_joint
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Fabrication_joint_mim.fabrication_joint">
<p>

A <b>fabrication_joint</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect"/> and a  <express_ref linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship"/> that implements the ARM concept
of  <express_ref linkend="Fabrication_joint:arm:Fabrication_joint_arm.Fabrication_joint"/>.
</p></ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: fabrication_joint.WR1
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Fabrication_joint_mim.fabrication_joint.wr:WR1">
The <b>fabrication_joint</b> <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.relating_shape_aspect"/> attribute shall relate to exactly one <express_ref linkend="component_feature:mim:Component_feature_mim.component_terminal">component_terminals</express_ref> that have a description of 'via terminal', 'printed component join terminal', 'non functional land join terminal', 'land join terminal', 'conductive interconnect element terminal', or 'component termination passage join terminal' to specify the 'fabrication features'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: fabrication_joint.WR2
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Fabrication_joint_mim.fabrication_joint.wr:WR2">
The <b>fabrication_joint</b> <express_ref 
linkend="product_property_definition_schema:ir_express:product_property_definition_schema.shape_aspect_relationship.related_shape_aspect"/> attribute shall relate to exactly one <express_ref linkend="component_feature:mim:Component_feature_mim.component_terminal">component_terminals</express_ref> that have a description of 'via terminal', 'printed component join terminal', 'non functional land join terminal', 'land join terminal', 'conductive interconnect element terminal', or 'component termination passage join terminal' to specify the 'fabrication features'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: fabrication_joint.WR3
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Fabrication_joint_mim.fabrication_joint.wr:WR3">
The <b>fabrication_joint</b> shall relate to either at most one land or to at most one  <express_ref linkend="Physical_unit_design_view:mim:Physical_unit_design_view_mim.component_definition"/> that has a description of 'stratum feature template component', to specify the 'auxiliary joint material'.
</ext_description>

<!-- ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
WR: fabrication_joint.WR4
++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++ -->
<ext_description linkend="Fabrication_joint_mim.fabrication_joint.wr:WR4">
The <b>fabrication_joint</b> shall not participate in a cyclic relationship.
</ext_description>

